# BauldAI

## Installation

1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/jimmydahiya/BauldAI.git
```

2. Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

3. Create a `.env` file

```env
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_api_key
```

4. Start the server

```bash
npm start
```

5. Open your browser

```
http://localhost:3000
```
